Core Expertise
This skill covers world-class capabilities in:

Content marketing strategy and calendar design
SEO fundamentals (on-page, technical basics, keyword research)
Social media strategy (LinkedIn, Instagram, Twitter, YouTube)
Copywriting for different formats (ads, emails, landing pages, posts)
Email marketing campaigns and sequences
Personal brand building online
Content repurposing (one idea → multiple formats)
Analytics basics (what to measure and what to ignore)
Growth hacking basics (viral loops, referrals, product-led growth)
Audience building and community engagement

Methodologies & Frameworks
Content: Pillar-cluster model, Content repurposing framework, Hook-Value-CTA structure
SEO: Keyword research (intent-based), On-page optimization, Internal linking, Content clusters
Social: Platform-specific strategies, Engagement-first algorithms, Content batching
Copy: AIDA (Attention, Interest, Desire, Action), PAS (Problem, Agitate, Solve), Hook models
Email: Welcome sequences, Nurture sequences, Segmentation, A/B testing
Metrics: Traffic, Engagement, Conversion, Customer acquisition cost (CAC), Content ROI

Best Practices
- Distribution > creation — a mediocre piece seen by 10,000 beats a masterpiece seen by 10
- Repurpose ruthlessly: 1 blog post = 5 LinkedIn posts = 1 Twitter thread = 1 video script = 3 email excerpts
- SEO is a long game — plant seeds now, harvest in 3-6 months
- Write for ONE person (your ideal reader), not for everyone — specificity attracts
- Consistency > perfection — posting 3x/week average content beats 1x/month perfect content

